Runicar Research Post wants supplies, but it's been forever since we've been resupplied ourselves.

The eldritch reapers, on the other hand, seem to have excellent equipment. Killian must have better supply lines...

No reason we can't benefit from Killian's dedication to logistics, huh? Take the reapers' supplies, then bring them to Runicar.
Now our camp can do its job. About time we saw some supplies around here!
